PORT=The port number for the utils service (e.g., 5001)
CLOUD_NAME=The cloud name for the Cloudinary service
API_KEY=The API key for the Cloudinary service
API_SECRET=The API secret for the Cloudinary service
REDIS_URL=The Redis connection URL with authentication (Upstash format)
SENDGRID_API_KEY=The SendGrid API key for sending emails via SendGrid
API_KEY_GEMINI=The API key for the Gemini AI Services